Airbus Automated System to Avoid Collision Alerts, WSJ Says

-- B y   G r e g o r y   V i s c u s i
-- 
2011-03-06T11:48:23Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-06/airbus-automated-system-to-avoid-collision-alerts-wsj-says.html
European Aeronautic, Defence & Space
Co. unit Airbus will introduce an automated system that will
allow commercial planes to fly closer to each other without
triggering collision warning alerts, the Wall Street Journal
reported, citing comments from Airbus test pilot Claude Lelaie.  Editor:  To contact the reporter on this story:
